snippet.title: Botany Manor – Release Date Trailer – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Botany Manor is coming to Nintendo Switch on April 9th: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/botany-manor-switch/ 

Set in a historical English homestead brimming with a lifetime of memorabilia and research to explore, take on the role of retired botanist Arabella Greene, uncover long-forgotten seeds, and piece together clues to solve puzzles to help each rare plant grow! 

#BotanyManor #NintendoSwitch 

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot

Visit Nintendo.com for all the latest! https://www.nintendo.com/us/
